{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以窮蒼和啟明星盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"你怎能知道啟明星是什麼？"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"是那燦爛的明星。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"每個人，都有一個保護者。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"人應當想一想，他自己是用什麼造成的？"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他是射出的精液造成的。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"那精液是從脊柱和肋骨之間發出的。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"真主確是能使他復原的，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"那是在一切秘密被揭穿之日。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"他絕沒有能力，也沒有援助者。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"以含雨的雲"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"和有縫的地發誓，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"這確是分別真偽的言辭，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"這不是笑話。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"他們必定要用計謀，"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"我也要用計謀。"},{"SurahNumber":86,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"所以你當寬限不信道的人們，你當寬限他們一下。"}]}